{"tid":2179482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★5個檢測中心首日預約爆滿---尚德邨、油塘、秀茂坪、石籬、馬鞍山","createTime":"2020-08-29T06:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T08:47:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"64ac79d5b51ffcb0c6c1eb6ab30b946cc0dd5d48","tid":2179482,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T06:47:09.000Z","msg":"至少5個檢測中心首日預約爆滿。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘區方面，油塘社區會堂及秀茂坪社區會堂亦較為爆滿，現時已無法預約兩個中心於9月1日的任何時段，而9月2日亦只餘下少量傍晚時段可供選擇。<br />\n<br />\n離島區僅於東涌文東路體育館設有檢測中心，該中心於9月1日的所有時段已爆滿；葵青區石籬社區會堂、沙田區馬鞍山體育館兩個中心於9月1日全日的所有時段亦已無法預約。<br />\n<br />\n另外，記者發現市民傾向預約上午時段檢測，不少中心在9月1日的上午時段都已爆滿。<br />\n<br />\nh[img]ttps://<a href=\"http://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5166088/org/21fc4b4a445522405256aed0a3c9ced0.jpg/Ope71F88eLg1v3vHKFhf5YGcdE5oFd4ZYbub3WG7m90?v=w1280r16_9[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5166088%2Forg%2F21fc4b4a445522405256aed0a3c9ced0.jpg%2FOpe71F88eLg1v3vHKFhf5YGcdE5oFd4ZYbub3WG7m90%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=9251dc51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5166088/org/21fc4b4a445522405256aed0a3c9ced0.jpg/Ope71F88eLg1v3vHKFhf5YGcdE5oFd4ZYbub3WG7m90?v=w1280r16_9[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/516997/%E5%B0%9A%E5%BE%B7foodpanda%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E6%9F%93%E7%96%AB-%E9%82%A8%E5%85%A7%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E9%A6%96%E5%85%A9%E5%A4%A9%E9%A0%90%E7%B4%84%E7%88%86%E6%BB%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F516997%2F%25E5%25B0%259A%25E5%25BE%25B7foodpanda%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E9%2582%25A8%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E4%25B8%25AD%2